## Scenario 10 — system bootstrap (ACC-010)

Not an HTTP endpoint. Exactly one Administrator account must exist before
the system accepts its first request. Per Archive/Development/Database
§1.4, this document does not invent a real seed email/password — that's a
deployment-time secret set via the actual Flyway seed migration at
implementation time, not fabricated here.

